column1: '''Faniel''' was the daughter of [[Finwë]] and [[Indis]] in an apparently discarded concept of the legendarium<ref>{{PM
column2: XI}}</ref>. She had two brothers, [[Fingolfin]] and [[Finarfin]], and two sisters [[Findis]] and [[Finvain]] ([[Írimë]]). She did not leave [[Valinor]] during the [[Flight of the Noldor]].<ref>{{MR
